  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><br>■ Strategically Build Your Party and Deck</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/2811b9bd370efd2f00ef48bb296deb6a.poster.avif?t=1745075681\" width=604 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/2811b9bd370efd2f00ef48bb296deb6a.webm?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/2811b9bd370efd2f00ef48bb296deb6a.mp4?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Experiment with various party and card combinations to find the winning formula. <br>Assemble a party with your favorite characters, obtain rare cards, and enhance them to challenge the Student Council President with your unique strategy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ The Tyrannical Student Council President ≪Sibylla≫ </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/2da7b2b51b4de48274e51719429912ff.poster.avif?t=1745075681\" width=604 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/2da7b2b51b4de48274e51719429912ff.webm?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/2da7b2b51b4de48274e51719429912ff.mp4?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The witch ≪Lulu≫ has lost most of her magic after ≪Sibylla≫ stole her precious heirloom. Will ≪Lulu≫ defeat the Student Council officers and reclaim her heirloom?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ A Challenging Journey for the Troublemaker Witch ≪Lulu≫</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/1f0438bb1c0ae6d554fd14a6cda227e2.poster.avif?t=1745075681\" width=604 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/1f0438bb1c0ae6d554fd14a6cda227e2.webm?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/1f0438bb1c0ae6d554fd14a6cda227e2.mp4?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The path to the Student Council President is perilous. Fight monsters to obtain skill cards, acquire rare relics and scrolls from merchants, and grow stronger. Recruit fearsome Student Council officers to fight alongside you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Replayability</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/b7427aa8135477bee4a0b8efa6a61092.poster.avif?t=1745075681\" width=604 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/b7427aa8135477bee4a0b8efa6a61092.webm?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/b7427aa8135477bee4a0b8efa6a61092.mp4?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\tWith 6 playable characters, two modes, 140+ cards, and various monsters, relics, and scrolls, create your own strategies and compete with players worldwide via leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Various Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/9d0f74414ff1fcce796cb5c9550a6112.poster.avif?t=1745075681\" width=604 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/9d0f74414ff1fcce796cb5c9550a6112.webm?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/9d0f74414ff1fcce796cb5c9550a6112.mp4?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 'Story Mode' and 'Witch’s Tower Mode'</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 6 playable characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Over 165 cards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 64 unique monsters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 32 relics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 26 scrolls</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A leaderboard to compete with players worldwide based on scores </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><br>■ Strategically Build Your Party and Deck</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/2811b9bd370efd2f00ef48bb296deb6a.poster.avif?t=1745075681\" width=604 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/2811b9bd370efd2f00ef48bb296deb6a.webm?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/2811b9bd370efd2f00ef48bb296deb6a.mp4?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Experiment with various party and card combinations to find the winning formula. <br>Assemble a party with your favorite characters, obtain rare cards, and enhance them to challenge the Student Council President with your unique strategy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ The Tyrannical Student Council President ≪Sibylla≫ </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/2da7b2b51b4de48274e51719429912ff.poster.avif?t=1745075681\" width=604 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/2da7b2b51b4de48274e51719429912ff.webm?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/2da7b2b51b4de48274e51719429912ff.mp4?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The witch ≪Lulu≫ has lost most of her magic after ≪Sibylla≫ stole her precious heirloom. Will ≪Lulu≫ defeat the Student Council officers and reclaim her heirloom?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ A Challenging Journey for the Troublemaker Witch ≪Lulu≫</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/1f0438bb1c0ae6d554fd14a6cda227e2.poster.avif?t=1745075681\" width=604 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/1f0438bb1c0ae6d554fd14a6cda227e2.webm?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/1f0438bb1c0ae6d554fd14a6cda227e2.mp4?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The path to the Student Council President is perilous. Fight monsters to obtain skill cards, acquire rare relics and scrolls from merchants, and grow stronger. Recruit fearsome Student Council officers to fight alongside you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Replayability</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/b7427aa8135477bee4a0b8efa6a61092.poster.avif?t=1745075681\" width=604 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/b7427aa8135477bee4a0b8efa6a61092.webm?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/b7427aa8135477bee4a0b8efa6a61092.mp4?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\tWith 6 playable characters, two modes, 140+ cards, and various monsters, relics, and scrolls, create your own strategies and compete with players worldwide via leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Various Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/9d0f74414ff1fcce796cb5c9550a6112.poster.avif?t=1745075681\" width=604 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/9d0f74414ff1fcce796cb5c9550a6112.webm?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775360/extras/9d0f74414ff1fcce796cb5c9550a6112.mp4?t=1745075681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 'Story Mode' and 'Witch’s Tower Mode'</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 6 playable characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Over 165 cards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 64 unique monsters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 32 relics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 26 scrolls</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A leaderboard to compete with players worldwide based on scores </p>",
